// How to modify a wall function? //

1) Make a copy of the wall function directory most similar to the one to be implemented;

2) Rename the source and header files with the new name;

3) Change all text instances of the former wall function to the new one with: sed -i s/oldWallFunctionName/newWallFunctionName/g newWallFunctionName.H (also for the .C file)

4) Go to: cd $FOAM_SRC/TurbulenceModel/turbulenceModels/Make


